item.title: about me
item.description: Hey there! I hope you’re having a good day. My name is Zakatell and thank you for visiting my little corner on the internet. The ability to observe without evaluating is the highest form of intelligence. - Jiddu Krishnamurti - Indian Philosopher This quote is fascinating because it feels like a recursion. If you stumbled here, then you probably found my post intriguing or wanna know me a little.
